subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which emperor ruled during the Mughal rule in Rajasthan?
question_hi: मुगल के समय राजस्थान में कौन सा प्राज्ञानिक समाचार करता था ?
explanation_en: Alamgir was the emperor who ruled during the Mughal rule in Rajasthan. He is also known as Jehangir in Hindi. Rajasthan was part of the Mughal empire from the 16th century until the end of the empire in 1857.
